Classes in ZetaFish.Interfaces used by ZetaFish
ICardRequestResponseListener
          Interface to be implemented by those interested in CardRequestResponse objects sent from the server to the client and published by the implementation of INetworkManager.
IChatListener
          Interface to be implemented by those interested in chat messages sent from the server to the client and published by the implementation of INetworkManager.
INetworkManager
          Interface to Network Manager implementation.
IRemovePlayerListener
          Interface to be implemented by those interested in ZFRemovePlayer objects sent from the server to the client and published by the implementation of INetworkManager.
IServerErrorListener
          Interface to be implemented by those interested in error messages generated at the server and published by the implementations of INetworkManager.
IStatusListener
          Interface to be implemented by those interested in ZFStatus objects sent from the server to the client and published by the implementation of INetworkManager.
ITurnListener
          Interface to be implemented by those interested in being notified of the local player's turn and published by implementations of INetworkManager.
